description:
Does your kid not enjoy learning the times table from 1x1 to 10x10? With this game you can change this. 
Just tap on the right answer to forward the frog one lily towards the crown. 

Kids love to learn math with this app. A great time spender when waiting for meals in a restaurant, visiting the family or driving long distances. 

Features: 
-2 player mode - kid vs dad, a real challenge! 
-solo mode - play against computer of 3 different levels (baby, daddy, champion) 
-lovely graphics 
-catchy tune
